## team-app `.gitignore`

(Spring Boot 프로젝트 기준)

```gitignore
# IntelliJ
.idea/
*.iml

# VSCode
.vscode/

# STS / Eclipse
.project
.classpath
.settings/
.factorypath

# Mac
.DS_Store

# Windows
Thumbs.db

# Build
target/
build/

# Logs
*.log

# Env
.env

# Maven Wrapper
.mvn/wrapper/maven-wrapper.jar

# Java
*.class

# Docker
docker-compose.override.yml

# OS
*.swp
